dataIdInfo.idAbs: This line data layer represents roads for Sheboygan County, Wisconsin at year-end 2016. It is a feature dataset within the geodatabase 'Sheboygan_Roads_YE2016'. [Road segments representing centerlines of all roadways or carriageways in Sheboygan County. Typically, this information is compiled from orthoimagery or other aerial photography sources. This representation of the road centerlines support address geocoding and mapping. It also serves as a source for public works and other agencies that are responsible for the active management of the road network.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
